{"tid":1721460,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"戰爭已開始，我地聽下一生都係戰亂嘅人講過咩。","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:12:22.000Z","uid":317066,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b341df1c4e64f2a067827a8d216544a683d06205","tid":1721460,"uid":317066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"武田信玄：<br />\n人は城、人は石垣、人は堀、情けは味方、あだは敵なり。<br />\n (人是城池，人是石垣，人是護城河，有情則為友，有仇即為敵。)<br />\n毛魔：<br />\n存地失人，人地皆失；存人失地，人地皆得。<br />\n孟子：<br />\n民為貴，社稷次之，君為輕。<br />\n佢地都知人先係最重要，人先可以將信念永續落去。<br />\n信念不死，革命不亡。<br />\n手足莫輕易送頭，對家人數不減，我方義士人數會減，要有勇有謀。<br />\n你送頭，我地除左痛，仲會或多或少士氣沉。<br />\n我想講人先係一切，be water。<br />\n祝各位將寫名流青史嘅手足，武運昌隆！"},{"pid":"371528e51e1003861f6d6311756ba0c52d13f7de","tid":1721460,"uid":317066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"莫輕易送頭，留有之驅，燃革命之火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9537cfc1c30247c52d9f1b1b3956d93447d3a4","tid":1721460,"uid":77685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"各位手足係歷史上將會正名為暴民流寇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b689cb26eeef3a74b77302f109d40ae3dc5e1c","tid":1721460,"uid":284642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"美國想急過人權法案既原因就係唔想香港重現六四<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721439</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e165ae79e2f19aea5bab0bce585644203ee4e157","tid":1721460,"uid":317066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e9537cfc1c30247c52d9f1b1b3956d93447d3a4","tid":1721460,"uid":77685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"各位手足係歷史上將會正名為暴民流寇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />